        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Smaller Class Sizes for Students and Educators Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education to award grants for local educational agencies to reduce class sizes in the early elementary grades (grades K-3) in targeted public elementary schools by recruiting, hiring, and supporting qualified teachers.</p> <ul> <ul> </ul></ul>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
